And with it, they might just save themselves from extinction.In this new world, the mana tree has been reborn and all life is connected to it.

A power only those capable of drawing upon the ancient Mana Tree seem to have. And with it, they might just save themselves from extinction.In this new world, the mana tree has been reborn and all life is connected to it.
 Each person has a unique ability, and they will need to use that power to save the world. The story will take a group of teenagers who have been together since birth, and follow them through their years in high school. As they get older, the will learn more about their powers and how to use them. They will learn that there are people out there who want to take over the world and they will have to stop them. he people who have been chosen by the mana tree will all have different powers.
 The people will be able to use the mana tree power to fight off the bad forces. The people will have to fight against time because there are others who want to take over the world.

 Each person has a unique ability, and they will need to use that power to save the world. As they get older, the will learn more about their powers and how to use them.
